1
00:01:46,879 --> 00:01:47,760
Liang Shuo

2
00:01:48,239 --> 00:01:49,760
Don't think I don't know.

3
00:01:52,480 --> 00:01:53,519
Team Leader Chen

4
00:01:53,879 --> 00:01:55,040
Barking like a dog

5
00:01:55,359 --> 00:01:57,079
You should still keep your eyes open.

6
00:01:57,280 --> 00:02:00,040
If your teeth aren't strong, don't bite off more than you can chew.

7
00:02:00,319 --> 00:02:02,280
Even kids understand this.

8
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:04,359
Why can't you learn?

9
00:02:04,359 --> 00:02:05,239
Liang Shuo, you—

10
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:10,719
Director

11
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,039
Director

12
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:15,599
I have something important to report to you privately.

13
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,039
Director

14
00:02:20,479 --> 00:02:21,719
Team Leader Chen

15
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:24,000
You don't need to explain anymore.

16
00:02:24,599 --> 00:02:27,159
Your subordinate has just confessed.

17
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,960
You were at the scene.

18
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:30,479
All the assassination operations

19
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:32,439
were directed by you.

20
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:33,400
I—

21
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,120
Guards!

22
00:02:34,439 --> 00:02:35,960
Take him to the interrogation room.

23
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,039
Interrogate him thoroughly.

24
00:02:37,039 --> 00:02:37,840
Director

25
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:39,919
Director

26
00:02:40,080 --> 00:02:40,879
Move.

27
00:02:42,639 --> 00:02:43,439
Director

28
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:45,439
Director

29
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,759
Liang Shuo

30
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:53,680
Director

31
00:02:53,759 --> 00:02:54,960
I'm innocent, Director!

32
00:02:57,039 --> 00:02:58,080
Director Li

33
00:02:58,639 --> 00:03:00,560
You really are magnanimous.

34
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:01,719
If it were me,

35
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:04,560
I would have sent him straight to the execution ground.

36
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:07,919
This Chen Gengsheng

37
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:10,000
has also been with the Special Operations Headquarters for a long time.

38
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:12,840
Before everything is fully clarified,

39
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:16,159
I think we should be more cautious.

40
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,759
Spend a bit more time

41
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:19,039
to get to the bottom of the truth.

42
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:21,360
It's absolutely necessary.

43
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:23,319
Director Li

44
00:03:23,759 --> 00:03:25,319
When the investigation results are out,

45
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:27,360
please inform me as soon as possible.

46
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,439
After all, as the victim,

47
00:03:29,439 --> 00:03:30,800
I trust that Director Li

48
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,800
won't refuse my request.

49
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:35,080
Of course.

50
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,960
Internal transparency

51
00:03:38,319 --> 00:03:40,360
is our principle in investigations.

52
00:03:40,599 --> 00:03:41,360
Besides,

53
00:03:41,639 --> 00:03:43,719
Director Liang made a contribution today.

54
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,960
I will definitely be fair.

55
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,120
As for Chen Gengsheng,

56
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,719
leave him to me.

57
00:03:49,319 --> 00:03:50,120
Alright.

58
00:03:50,479 --> 00:03:51,879
It's getting late.

59
00:03:52,199 --> 00:03:53,280
Let's call it a day.

60
00:03:54,039 --> 00:03:55,120
As for what comes next,

61
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,280
let's discuss it tomorrow.

62
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,639
Gentlemen, may I ask who you are looking for?

63
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:29,600
Hello.

64
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:33,199
I am Takagi Yuyi from the Customs Investigation Bureau.

65
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:36,560
I am here on behalf of Director Mizuno of the Ume Agency.

66
00:04:36,959 --> 00:04:38,160
I have an appointment.

67
00:04:40,079 --> 00:04:40,920
Yes, yes.

68
00:04:41,199 --> 00:04:41,639
Who are you looking for?

69
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:42,800
I'll inform them for you.

70
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:44,920
Wang Qiaosu.

71
00:04:45,079 --> 00:04:46,120
Director Wang.

72
00:04:47,319 --> 00:04:47,879
He's on the second floor.

73
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:48,560
This way, please.

74
00:05:22,199 --> 00:05:22,680
This way.

75
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:30,079
Please.

76
00:05:30,079 --> 00:05:31,319
Director Wang, someone is here to see you.

77
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:32,879
Director Wang.

78
00:05:49,399 --> 00:05:50,120
Where is the person?

79
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:51,759
Where is he?

80
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:52,839
I don't know.

81
00:05:52,839 --> 00:05:54,000
He was just here a moment ago.

82
00:05:54,160 --> 00:05:54,639
Search.

83
00:05:58,399 --> 00:06:00,160
He left in a hurry.

84
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:03,360
Someone leaked information.

85
00:06:07,759 --> 00:06:09,800
Mr. Mizuno was right.

86
00:06:10,279 --> 00:06:13,920
The Peace Conference is about to begin.

87
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:19,120
We must not relax our supervision of key departments.

88
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:26,720
The location where the anti-Japanese elements are hiding explosives

89
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:33,279
is within the delivery area of this North Shanghai post office.

90
00:07:13,639 --> 00:07:15,160
We faced danger twice tonight.

91
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:17,680
It was all thanks to Director Liang risking his life to save us.

92
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,040
If it weren't for you,

93
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:19,959
Not at all.

94
00:07:20,319 --> 00:07:21,639
You're too kind, sir.

95
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:24,519
For Director Liang,

96
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,160
it might have been an easy task.

97
00:07:26,519 --> 00:07:28,040
But for Xizi,

98
00:07:28,399 --> 00:07:29,720
it was a lifesaving favor.

99
00:07:29,879 --> 00:07:31,319
I will never forget it.

100
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,199
Chief Hirata, you overstate it.

101
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,959
I was just performing my duty as an escort.

102
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:36,000
The responsibility is great.

103
00:07:36,199 --> 00:07:37,920
I was simply fulfilling my mission.

104
00:07:39,399 --> 00:07:42,079
The evidence against Chen Gengsheng is now conclusive.

105
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:43,560
It seems

106
00:07:44,199 --> 00:07:45,639
he is the one Director Liang

107
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,040
mentioned

108
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:48,959
as the mole within headquarters.

109
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:52,000
But what the truth really is

110
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:53,759
still depends on headquarters

111
00:07:53,759 --> 00:07:55,480
and the Special Affairs Committee's final decision.

112
00:07:56,319 --> 00:07:57,240
As for matters in the department,

113
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,800
there's no need to rush for now.

114
00:07:59,639 --> 00:08:02,160
Director Liang should get some rest now.

115
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:04,399
Thank you for your concern, sir.

116
00:08:04,839 --> 00:08:06,480
I still have a lot of work to handle.

117
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:07,759
If the work isn't finished,

118
00:08:07,959 --> 00:08:09,600
it's hard to feel at ease.

119
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,600
Within headquarters,

120
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:13,800
if everyone were as dedicated as Director Liang,

121
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,759
diligently fulfilling their duties,

122
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:17,879
then our goal of establishing Greater East Asia Co-Prosperity

123
00:08:17,879 --> 00:08:19,160
would soon be within reach.

124
00:08:19,959 --> 00:08:21,560
Director Liang's achievements today

125
00:08:21,839 --> 00:08:24,519
will be fully reported to Mr. Mizuno.

126
00:08:26,199 --> 00:08:27,920
Thank you for your support, sir.

127
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:42,759
Teacher

128
00:08:42,759 --> 00:08:43,279
Junior Sister

129
00:08:43,279 --> 00:08:43,960
Senior Brother

130
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:45,159
Where did you put the explosives?

131
00:08:45,559 --> 00:08:47,519
At a transport company on Rui'an Road.

132
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,320
The goods are on a truck.

133
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:50,440
We didn't dare unload them.

134
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:51,759
They're covered with canvas.

135
00:08:51,759 --> 00:08:53,080
Disguised as construction materials.

136
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,799
Two of our brothers are watching over them.

137
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:55,799
If they're discovered,

138
00:08:55,799 --> 00:08:56,919
they can be moved at any time.

139
00:08:57,919 --> 00:08:59,399
You always handle things so reliably.

140
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:02,360
Although the venue for the Peace Conference

141
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:04,120
hasn't been finalized,

142
00:09:04,399 --> 00:09:05,960
it won't be outside the northern district of Shanghai.

143
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:10,759
These explosives

144
00:09:10,759 --> 00:09:12,519
can't all be transported there directly.

145
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:13,840
They need to be delivered in batches.

146
00:09:14,039 --> 00:09:14,960
Be ready to act at any time.

147
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:19,360
Teacher

148
00:09:19,519 --> 00:09:20,600
How should we distribute the explosives?

149
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:22,679
Use the postal route.

150
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,879
Send them through regular delivery channels.

151
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:27,639
I've already prepared a family letter for the director

152
00:09:27,639 --> 00:09:28,519
Wang Qiaosu

153
00:09:28,559 --> 00:09:30,039
of the northern Shanghai postal branch.

154
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,440
Once he sees the letter,

155
00:09:31,519 --> 00:09:32,320
he'll make the arrangements.

156
00:09:32,759 --> 00:09:33,480
Sir

157
00:09:34,679 --> 00:09:35,399
Sir

158
00:09:35,559 --> 00:09:36,799
There's been an incident at the northern Shanghai post office.

159
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,480
The post office contact reported

160
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:41,120
that the Japanese just raided the post office.

161
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:41,879
They said

162
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,519
they were looking for Director Wang Qiaosu to talk.

163
00:09:43,679 --> 00:09:45,080
Director Wang sensed something was wrong

164
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,120
and left early.

165
00:09:46,279 --> 00:09:48,399
The Japanese, in their anger, even killed the gatekeeper.

166
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:56,679
Postal route

167
00:09:56,679 --> 00:09:58,799
is the weakest link in the entire plan.

168
00:09:59,279 --> 00:10:00,840
There is a lot of coming and going of people.

169
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,279
It's the hardest to withstand investigation.

170
00:10:03,279 --> 00:10:03,960
I didn't expect it.

171
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:06,000
The part I worried about the most still had a problem.

172
00:10:06,879 --> 00:10:08,840
Mizuno Shingen must have been watching

173
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:10,320
Wang Qiaosu's line for a while.

174
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:12,200
That's why the military police reacted so quickly.

175
00:10:15,519 --> 00:10:17,320
Fortunately, Wang Qiaosu has already escaped.

176
00:10:19,879 --> 00:10:21,919
We can only prepare for the worst.

177
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:24,360
Try to contact Liang Shuo.

178
00:10:24,679 --> 00:10:25,399
I want to see him.

179
00:10:26,759 --> 00:10:27,159
Okay.

180
00:10:29,279 --> 00:10:30,759
Newspapers for sale! Newspapers for sale!

181
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:32,919
Get your newspapers! Get your newspapers!

182
00:10:32,919 --> 00:10:33,960
Current Affairs News

183
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:35,519
Come here, child.

184
00:10:35,679 --> 00:10:36,600
Buy a newspaper.

185
00:10:36,759 --> 00:10:37,559
Sir, here you go.

186
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,120
Thank you, sir.

187
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:45,279
Newspapers for sale! Newspapers for sale!

188
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:48,440
Take a look at this news.

189
00:10:53,159 --> 00:10:54,200
The mail route has been destroyed.

190
00:10:55,039 --> 00:10:56,279
Wang Qiaosu has escaped.

191
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,120
Mizuno Shingen.

192
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,399
This move uses offense as defense.

193
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:02,879
It's truly impressive.

194
00:11:04,639 --> 00:11:06,480
Even someone like Xie Jun'an

195
00:11:07,399 --> 00:11:09,039
has gotten caught up in this.

196
00:11:11,879 --> 00:11:13,000
What should we do about this?

197
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:16,120
Although this is an issue for the Military Bureau of Investigation and Statistics,

198
00:11:16,799 --> 00:11:18,720
we can't possibly cooperate with them.

199
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:20,399
However,

200
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:23,039
if their operation is put on hold,

201
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:25,799
the Japanese will turn their attention elsewhere.

202
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:28,360
This will definitely affect our rescue plan.

203
00:11:29,799 --> 00:11:30,600
Moreover,

204
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:32,200
I'm also worried

205
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:33,919
because Wang Qiaosu has a special status.

206
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:36,120
If he falls into the hands of the Japanese,

207
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:38,559
it could threaten Comrade Qingshuang's undercover mission

208
00:11:38,559 --> 00:11:39,559
and put it at risk.

209
00:11:47,279 --> 00:11:48,679
Your concern

210
00:11:49,159 --> 00:11:50,240
is not unfounded.

211
00:11:52,399 --> 00:11:54,200
I request that the organization pay attention to this matter.

212
00:11:56,919 --> 00:11:57,480
Alright.

213
00:11:57,919 --> 00:11:58,600
I will immediately

214
00:11:58,840 --> 00:12:00,000
report this to the organization.

215
00:12:00,559 --> 00:12:01,639
If there is any news,

216
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,679
I will send someone to contact you.

217
00:12:18,639 --> 00:12:20,360
Didn't you have something to say to me?

218
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:23,159
I'm giving you the chance right now.

219
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:25,799
Director.

220
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:28,879
You have to trust me.

221
00:12:29,200 --> 00:12:31,360
I've always been loyal.

222
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:33,399
It's just that this time,

223
00:12:34,799 --> 00:12:36,559
I was set up by Liang Shuo.

224
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,519
Director, you know that.

225
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:41,399
I've always suspected Liang Shuo.

226
00:12:43,559 --> 00:12:46,200
So after Liang Shuo came back on the 18th,

227
00:12:47,159 --> 00:12:49,000
I've been keeping an eye on him.

228
00:12:50,559 --> 00:12:52,120
During the previous headquarters gathering,

229
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:54,440
I had someone pose as a Chongqing agent.

230
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:55,480
To make contact with him.

231
00:12:55,879 --> 00:12:57,960
The meeting place was Jiangfeng Restaurant.

232
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,639
He was informed of the meeting time.

233
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:01,639
It was 8 o'clock last night.

234
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:05,120
You mean,

235
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:08,200
Liang Shuo knew about Jiangfeng Restaurant?

236
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:10,799
Yes.

237
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:13,720
I have a recording of this.

238
00:13:13,879 --> 00:13:15,120
It can be used as evidence.

239
00:13:15,399 --> 00:13:16,919
Then why didn't you say anything last night?

240
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:20,279
Liang Shuo doesn't know I have a recording.

241
00:13:23,559 --> 00:13:25,600
This person is good at twisting the truth.

242
00:13:25,600 --> 00:13:27,039
He's way too cunning.

243
00:13:28,399 --> 00:13:29,919
I need to let you know first.

244
00:13:30,559 --> 00:13:31,600
Director, think about it.

245
00:13:32,879 --> 00:13:34,279
Liang Shuo knows very well

246
00:13:34,279 --> 00:13:37,120
that he was supposed to meet the Chongqing agents at Jiangfeng Restaurant.

247
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:38,919
But he knew and didn't report it.

248
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:40,519
What does that tell us?

249
00:13:40,759 --> 00:13:43,240
At the very least, it suggests he might be covering for them.

250
00:13:44,159 --> 00:13:46,200
And this time, not only did he not report it,

251
00:13:46,279 --> 00:13:47,960
he even tried to frame me instead.

252
00:13:48,639 --> 00:13:50,000
What does that mean?

253
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:53,960
It means Liang Shuo saw through your plan.

254
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:55,600
And he didn't report it.

255
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:57,759
Instead, at the same time,

256
00:13:58,360 --> 00:14:01,600
he was active near Jiangfeng Restaurant.

257
00:14:02,120 --> 00:14:03,240
That's right.

258
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:05,559
I can't outsmart him.

259
00:14:05,879 --> 00:14:07,879
There's definitely something wrong with Liang Shuo.

260
00:14:12,039 --> 00:14:13,039
What about the recording?

261
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:27,320
Morning.

262
00:14:27,919 --> 00:14:29,000
You're here so early.

263
00:14:29,120 --> 00:14:30,440
Chen Gengsheng has already been interrogated.

264
00:14:30,679 --> 00:14:31,679
Let's talk as we walk.

265
00:14:32,519 --> 00:14:34,120
I don't know what the Director is thinking either.

266
00:14:34,279 --> 00:14:35,279
He specifically named you.

267
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:37,039
He wants you to interrogate Chen Gengsheng personally.

268
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:41,159
The Director knows I don't get along with him.

269
00:14:41,279 --> 00:14:42,919
Is he trying to make me go all out against him?

270
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:44,200
Brother Cui,

271
00:14:44,559 --> 00:14:45,960
you'd better think this through.

272
00:14:46,639 --> 00:14:47,559
Don't overthink it.

273
00:14:47,600 --> 00:14:48,600
This also shows

274
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:49,720
that the Director trusts you.

275
00:14:58,600 --> 00:14:59,279
Director

276
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:01,399
Found in Chief Chen's office

277
00:15:01,840 --> 00:15:02,600
Put it over there

278
00:15:02,879 --> 00:15:03,480
Okay

279
00:15:06,320 --> 00:15:06,960
Director

280
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:08,840
Are you suspecting Liang Shuo

281
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:10,279
or Chen Gengsheng

282
00:15:13,639 --> 00:15:16,440
Until someone can prove their innocence

283
00:15:18,720 --> 00:15:19,879
I don't trust anyone

