00:26:45,480 --> 00:26:47,039
you were already furious.

574
00:26:47,519 --> 00:26:48,400
I thought

575
00:26:48,400 --> 00:26:50,319
there was no need to trouble you with unnecessary worries.

576
00:26:51,720 --> 00:26:53,160
How grand and dignified your words sound.

577
00:26:53,160 --> 00:26:54,359
The more you try to cover it up, the more obvious it becomes.

578
00:26:55,680 --> 00:26:56,400
Director,

579
00:26:56,720 --> 00:26:57,799
it's not for anything else.

580
00:26:58,039 --> 00:27:00,000
The brothers working under us

581
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:01,599
are all risking their lives.

582
00:27:01,599 --> 00:27:03,000
I have to let them get a little benefit, don't I?

583
00:27:03,039 --> 00:27:04,200
Would I let her succeed?

584
00:27:06,559 --> 00:27:07,960
So, Director Cui,

585
00:27:08,960 --> 00:27:10,519
you really are selfless, aren't you?

586
00:27:11,640 --> 00:27:13,519
All the mistakes are my fault.

587
00:27:13,519 --> 00:27:14,480
Please punish me, Director.

588
00:27:14,480 --> 00:27:15,599
Don't play these tricks with me.

589
00:27:16,079 --> 00:27:17,160
If you hide things from me again,

590
00:27:17,160 --> 00:27:18,039
if you dare do it again,

591
00:27:18,039 --> 00:27:19,200
there absolutely won't be a next time.

592
00:27:23,559 --> 00:27:25,480
The way to deceive Hirata Xizi

593
00:27:26,240 --> 00:27:27,440
was taught to you by Liang Shuo.

594
00:27:29,240 --> 00:27:30,039
Yes.

595
00:27:30,880 --> 00:27:32,440
Why did he want to help you?

596
00:27:33,119 --> 00:27:34,599
What exactly is he after?

597
00:27:35,400 --> 00:27:36,079
Director.

598
00:27:36,319 --> 00:27:37,599
Liang Shuo has done enough for these brothers—

599
00:27:37,599 --> 00:27:38,359
Shut up.

600
00:27:38,640 --> 00:27:40,799
Don't talk to me about this disgusting brotherhood nonsense.

601
00:27:43,960 --> 00:27:44,759
Director.

602
00:27:45,200 --> 00:27:46,000
If you really think

603
00:27:46,000 --> 00:27:47,400
Liang Shuo is still a suspect,

604
00:27:47,400 --> 00:27:49,000
then bring him here and confront him face to face.

605
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:49,680
You—

606
00:27:50,279 --> 00:27:51,160
You...

607
00:27:58,160 --> 00:27:59,200
Hello, Director Liang.

608
00:28:23,079 --> 00:28:24,559
Director Liang, what brings you here?

609
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:26,000
I want to see the Director.

610
00:28:32,319 --> 00:28:33,160
Director.

611
00:28:33,440 --> 00:28:34,599
Director Liang requests to see you.

612
00:28:35,799 --> 00:28:36,599
Please.

613
00:28:38,880 --> 00:28:39,720
Director.

614
00:28:39,720 --> 00:28:40,839
Then I'll excuse myself for now.

615
00:28:41,160 --> 00:28:41,880
Go ahead.

616
00:28:41,880 --> 00:28:42,920
Director Liang.

617
00:28:43,039 --> 00:28:43,799
Please.

618
00:28:46,839 --> 00:28:47,839
Director Liang

619
00:28:47,839 --> 00:28:48,400
Come

620
00:28:48,599 --> 00:28:49,400
Have a seat

621
00:28:49,960 --> 00:28:50,799
Director Xie

622
00:28:50,960 --> 00:28:52,200
I heard from Secretary Wang

623
