that you have something to report to me

624
00:28:56,799 --> 00:28:59,440
Team Leader Chen installed surveillance equipment at No. 76 without authorization

625
00:28:59,599 --> 00:29:00,839
The director doesn't want to pursue the matter

626
00:29:01,160 --> 00:29:02,559
But I don't want to let him off

627
00:29:02,720 --> 00:29:03,519
Liang Shuo

628
00:29:04,200 --> 00:29:06,240
You're getting bolder and bolder

629
00:29:07,759 --> 00:29:09,960
What makes you say I don't want to pursue it?

630
00:29:12,559 --> 00:29:13,759
Forgive my rudeness

631
00:29:14,200 --> 00:29:15,000
What is it?

632
00:29:15,839 --> 00:29:17,440
Is there something you can't say?

633
00:29:18,880 --> 00:29:20,559
I dare to ask

634
00:29:21,400 --> 00:29:22,319
All this time

635
00:29:22,799 --> 00:29:24,759
How have I performed at No. 76?

636
00:29:25,000 --> 00:29:26,480
You have always been

637
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:27,839
my most capable subordinate

638
00:29:28,359 --> 00:29:29,519
without exception

639
00:29:29,599 --> 00:29:32,039
Then why has the director never trusted me?

640
00:29:33,119 --> 00:29:34,440
What are you talking about?

641
00:29:34,680 --> 00:29:36,039
If the director trusted me

642
00:29:36,200 --> 00:29:37,839
you wouldn't have sent someone to test me

643
00:29:38,119 --> 00:29:40,559
