644
00:29:40,559 --> 00:29:41,599
Nonsense

645
00:29:41,759 --> 00:29:42,799
Chen Gengsheng monitoring you

646
00:29:42,799 --> 00:29:44,400
That wasn't my order

647
00:29:44,720 --> 00:29:46,599
And you say I sent someone to test you

648
00:29:46,640 --> 00:29:48,119
That's pure nonsense

649
00:29:50,440 --> 00:29:52,759
Disguising as a Chongqing agent to contact you

650
00:29:52,759 --> 00:29:54,440
Wasn't that your instruction?

651
00:29:54,519 --> 00:29:55,599
Of course not

652
00:29:55,680 --> 00:29:56,839
I only found out today

653
00:29:56,880 --> 00:29:58,799
I just learned about this today

654
00:30:01,400 --> 00:30:02,599
So in that case

655
00:30:03,920 --> 00:30:05,359
it was Chen Gengsheng himself

656
00:30:08,720 --> 00:30:10,039
You've blamed the wrong person

657
00:30:14,319 --> 00:30:15,119
That's right.

658
00:30:15,960 --> 00:30:16,960
At the banquet that day,

659
00:30:17,640 --> 00:30:18,640
this person was in the restroom

660
00:30:18,640 --> 00:30:20,599
and said a bunch of confusing things to me.

661
00:30:20,920 --> 00:30:22,799
I always thought it was on your orders.

662
00:30:23,359 --> 00:30:24,720
So,

663
00:30:24,720 --> 00:30:26,359
