664
00:30:27,240 --> 00:30:28,559
If the director wanted to investigate me,

665
00:30:29,119 --> 00:30:30,599
how would I dare to get involved?

666
00:30:30,720 --> 00:30:32,200
He said he saw through the setup.

667
00:30:32,559 --> 00:30:35,400
All I could do was keep my head down and do my job.

668
00:30:41,319 --> 00:30:42,839
Then why

669
00:30:42,839 --> 00:30:44,400
did you and Hirata Noriko

670
00:30:44,720 --> 00:30:46,160
go to

671
00:30:46,400 --> 00:30:48,640
the Lianjia Alley warehouse at that time?

672
00:30:50,759 --> 00:30:51,799
I deserve to be punished.

673
00:30:51,799 --> 00:30:53,400
I tried to be clever with you.

674
00:30:53,839 --> 00:30:54,519
What?

675
00:30:54,519 --> 00:30:55,119
Speak.

676
00:30:55,599 --> 00:30:56,759
What I thought was,

677
00:30:56,960 --> 00:30:58,000
as long as I was with Officer Hirata

678
00:30:58,000 --> 00:30:59,559
at that time,

679
00:31:00,160 --> 00:31:02,119
she would naturally help clear my name.

680
00:31:03,759 --> 00:31:06,240
Director Liang, you really are cunning.

681
00:31:06,319 --> 00:31:07,640
Such a schemer.

682
00:31:08,559 --> 00:31:09,279
Alright then.

683
00:31:09,279 --> 00:31:10,400
It was all a misunderstanding.

684
00:31:11,279 --> 00:31:12,920
These past two days, because of this matter,

685
00:31:12,960 --> 00:31:14,319
I've been tossing and turning.

686
00:31:14,640 --> 00:31:16,000
It wasn't until just now, when Director Cui

687
00:31:16,279 --> 00:31:18,319
mentioned Chen Gengsheng eavesdropping on me,

688
00:31:18,319 --> 00:31:19,799
that I finally gathered the courage

689
00:31:19,799 --> 00:31:21,119
to ask you for confirmation.

690
00:31:21,680 --> 00:31:22,480
Don't worry.

691
00:31:22,720 --> 00:31:25,319
Once it's confirmed that Chen Gengsheng is anti-Japanese,

692
00:31:26,400 --> 00:31:29,240
I'll personally take care of him.

693
00:31:54,279 --> 00:31:55,000
Director

694
00:31:55,000 --> 00:31:55,720
What do you think?

695
00:31:56,839 --> 00:31:57,640
It seems

696
00:31:58,200 --> 00:31:59,960
we really misunderstood Liang Shuo.

697
00:32:00,440 --> 00:32:01,799
He can be so calm about it.

698
00:32:01,880 --> 00:32:03,680
I really don't think there's anything wrong with Liang Shuo.

699
00:32:04,359 --> 00:32:05,160
You

700
00:32:05,880 --> 00:32:06,799
