701
00:32:06,799 --> 00:32:07,480
Yes.

702
00:32:08,960 --> 00:32:11,119
We've been dogs for the Japanese for so many years,

703
00:32:11,440 --> 00:32:13,119
and now even the bone scraps in our mouths

704
00:32:13,119 --> 00:32:14,200
are being picked out.

705
00:32:14,519 --> 00:32:15,880
That Hirata and Mizuno

706
00:32:15,880 --> 00:32:17,559
are really going too far.

707
00:32:17,920 --> 00:32:18,799
It seems

708
00:32:18,799 --> 00:32:20,319
that dogs who are too loyal

709
00:32:20,640 --> 00:32:22,599
shouldn't even expect a sip of soup.

710
00:32:22,640 --> 00:32:23,440
Please calm your anger.

711
00:32:23,559 --> 00:32:25,359
I will definitely help share your burdens.

712
00:32:26,240 --> 00:32:29,119
The anti-Japanese elements are targeting the Peace Conference directly.

713
00:32:29,559 --> 00:32:30,480
So,

714
00:32:30,599 --> 00:32:32,359
we still need to be cautious.

715
00:32:32,680 --> 00:32:34,400
We absolutely cannot tie our security and leverage

716
00:32:34,440 --> 00:32:36,400
to the Japanese.

717
00:32:36,880 --> 00:32:37,799
As for Liang Shuo,

718
00:32:38,319 --> 00:32:41,200
he is a key candidate for the Peace Conference's security.

719
00:32:41,359 --> 00:32:43,720
We need to investigate him further.

720
00:32:43,920 --> 00:32:45,920
The appointment from the Central Executive Committee

721
00:32:45,920 --> 00:32:46,759
