722
00:32:46,759 --> 00:32:48,400
It's not that easy.

723
00:32:49,319 --> 00:32:51,000
This Special Inspector position

724
00:32:51,039 --> 00:32:52,160
is too delicate.

725
00:32:52,440 --> 00:32:55,400
It involves our maneuvering at the Peace Conference,

726
00:32:55,880 --> 00:32:57,720
