730
00:33:03,200 --> 00:33:04,119
On our side,

731
00:33:04,119 --> 00:33:05,440
we need Director Ding's approval.

732
00:33:05,559 --> 00:33:06,799
On the Japanese side,

733
00:33:06,799 --> 00:33:08,519
it requires Mizuno Nobukage's endorsement.

734
00:33:10,119 --> 00:33:11,759
This is really complicated.

735
00:33:12,440 --> 00:33:13,400
As for this matter,

736
00:33:13,519 --> 00:33:14,759
we still need to plan carefully.

737
00:33:15,160 --> 00:33:17,759
I'll also make further suggestions to Director Ding.

738
00:33:18,559 --> 00:33:19,359
And another thing,

739
00:33:19,559 --> 00:33:21,200
the person I initially recommended to the higher-ups

740
00:33:21,200 --> 00:33:22,039
was you.

741
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:23,000
But you,

742
00:33:23,440 --> 00:33:25,319
can't even maintain good relations with the Japanese.

743
00:33:25,799 --> 00:33:26,799
You're disappointing.

744
00:33:27,079 --> 00:33:28,119
It's my own incompetence.

745
00:33:28,400 --> 00:33:29,559
I still prefer

746
00:33:29,559 --> 00:33:30,960
to serve by your side, Director.

747
00:33:44,119 --> 00:33:45,839
If you ever need to contact me urgently,

748
00:33:46,240 --> 00:33:48,359
go to the balcony across from the Special Agent Headquarters

749
00:33:48,359 --> 00:33:49,519
and place a pot of orchids there.

750
00:33:56,960 --> 00:33:57,799
On the mail route,

751
00:33:58,200 --> 00:33:59,920
