752
00:33:59,920 --> 00:34:01,319
He might reveal

753
00:34:01,319 --> 00:34:03,200
information about the Snow Blind Project.

754
00:34:03,960 --> 00:34:05,799
How much does he know about the operation?

755
00:34:07,519 --> 00:34:09,440
Scorpio wants to meet you this afternoon.

756
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:11,599
Understood.

757
00:34:11,599 --> 00:34:12,599
You can go back first.

758
00:34:12,599 --> 00:34:13,400
Alright.

759
00:35:15,360 --> 00:35:16,840
You coming to find me on your own

