794
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:03,480
The Japanese have long suspected

795
00:37:03,480 --> 00:37:05,000
there's an undercover agent in Unit 76.

796
00:37:05,280 --> 00:37:06,000
Right now, I don't know

797
00:37:06,000 --> 00:37:07,840
how much inside information Wang Qiaosu actually knows.

798
00:37:08,400 --> 00:37:09,880
But Mizuno Nobukage

799
00:37:09,880 --> 00:37:11,440
