819
00:37:48,920 --> 00:37:49,719
At the same time,

820
00:37:49,840 --> 00:37:51,039
we need to fake

821
00:37:51,039 --> 00:37:52,760
a connection between Chen Gengsheng and Wang Qiaosu.

822
00:37:52,760 --> 00:37:54,039
Drag Wang Qiaosu into this.

823
00:37:54,400 --> 00:37:55,280
How do we stop it?

824
00:38:07,559 --> 00:38:09,639
No. 76's hesitation about Chen Gengsheng

825
00:38:09,920 --> 00:38:11,440
