826
00:38:11,760 --> 00:38:14,000
I need to regain No. 76's trust.

827
00:38:14,280 --> 00:38:15,920
And resolve the current trouble at the same time.

828
00:38:15,920 --> 00:38:17,280
Eliminate Chen Gengsheng, this cancer.

829
00:38:17,280 --> 00:38:18,320
Why not do it?

830
00:38:20,480 --> 00:38:21,840
I will report it immediately.

831
00:38:21,840 --> 00:38:22,440
But

832
00:38:24,239 --> 00:38:25,519
But this plan is too big.

